but I really need her.

41:44.010 --> 41:47.427
You bother to check her out
before you got into all this?

41:47.510 --> 41:49.093
Obviously not enough.

41:49.176 --> 41:51.468
- Well, you should have.
- That's what you do.

41:52.927 --> 41:55.969
You ever hear of Featureflix?

41:56.051 --> 41:58.260
Seventy-five billion dollars
of Pacific's money

41:58.343 --> 42:01.385
to acquire the world's
largest streaming service.

42:01.468 --> 42:03.343
It'll be our growth driver.

42:05.010 --> 42:07.135
Doug was the only hold out,

42:07.218 --> 42:09.051
and now that we've acquired it,

42:09.135 --> 42:10.969
we need a specific piece
of property,

42:11.051 --> 42:14.468
85 acres, publicly owned,
to house it.

42:14.552 --> 42:16.427
You know what's on it now?

42:17.969 --> 42:19.427
A prison.

42:19.510 --> 42:21.385
So I made an offer.

42:21.468 --> 42:23.468
A fair offer.

42:23.552 --> 42:25.677
The mayor blocked it.

42:34.010 --> 42:37.468
Hundred thousand dollars
every week until the election.

42:37.552 --> 42:40.135
Once she's elected,
I double it.

42:42.760 --> 42:45.719
You look like shit.
I'll get you a drink.

42:47.176 --> 42:49.093
Sit down.

42:56.176 --> 42:59.301
[liquor pouring]

43:02.927 --> 43:05.301
[groans]

43:14.885 --> 43:17.176
There's something I've been
meaning to ask you,

43:17.260 --> 43:19.093
and it's none of my business,

43:19.176 --> 43:22.760
so you don't have to answer
if you don't want to, but...

43:22.844 --> 43:25.093
- That night--
- I was tired.

43:27.260 --> 43:28.969
Tired?

43:31.927 --> 43:33.635
I just...

43:37.218 --> 43:39.677
I just wanted it all to stop.

43:41.969 --> 43:43.760
And then there she was.

43:43.844 --> 43:45.343
Who?

43:47.093 --> 43:48.510
Abby.

43:50.719 --> 43:53.343
Like she'd been there
all along, you know?

43:56.635 --> 43:58.427
And I--

43:58.510 --> 44:00.385
I started to think...

44:03.385 --> 44:05.218
that without her...

44:07.301 --> 44:09.635
there wasn't much for me,
you know?

44:13.010 --> 44:15.885
♪ dramatic music ♪

44:15.969 --> 44:20.844
♪♪♪

44:24.135 --> 44:25.969
Look at me.

44:28.093 --> 44:29.677
I'm glad you're here.

44:29.760 --> 44:32.135
I'm glad you're not dead.

44:37.885 --> 44:40.385
You and me, Ray...

44:40.468 --> 44:42.218
we're gonna make a mayor.

44:47.343 --> 44:49.719
[groans]

44:49.802 --> 44:54.927
♪♪♪

45:09.802 --> 45:12.719
[woman speaking indistinctly
on TV]

45:12.802 --> 45:17.927
♪♪♪

45:22.051 --> 45:24.343
Doctor come in,
or he move or anything?

45:24.427 --> 45:26.385
[guard] No, just
there like that.

45:26.468 --> 45:28.260
Brought you a hero.

45:28.343 --> 45:29.218
[grunts]

45:29.301 --> 45:30.844
Want one?

45:30.927 --> 45:32.510
Yours.

45:32.593 --> 45:34.301
Thanks.

45:34.385 --> 45:39.260
♪♪♪

45:51.969 --> 45:53.760
Excuse me, my man.

45:54.802 --> 45:56.593
Yeah, how can I help you?

45:56.677 --> 45:58.176
Um, I'm here to see my father.

45:58.260 --> 45:59.760
Uh, he was brought in
last night.

45:59.844 --> 46:01.468
His name's Mickey Donovan.

46:02.802 --> 46:04.927
- [computer beeps]
- Donovan?

46:09.260 --> 46:14.135
♪♪♪

46:34.719 --> 46:36.927
You got to put
your hands up, right?

46:37.010 --> 46:39.301
First thing you got to learn
is defense.

46:39.385 --> 46:42.218
- [Jimmy] Not punching?
- Defense first, kid.

46:42.301 --> 46:44.510
[punches thudding]

46:44.593 --> 46:47.802
Heard there was a fucked-up
drug deal downtown.

46:54.552 --> 46:56.176
Seems like
some Wall Street douchebag

46:56.260 --> 46:58.510
and his Samoan dealer
shot each other.

46:58.593 --> 47:01.010
Real John Wayne shit.

47:01.093 --> 47:02.552
Yeah.

47:06.093 --> 47:08.051
You all right, Ray?

47:09.051 --> 47:10.885
- Huh?
- Yeah, sure.

47:13.301 --> 47:16.093
I'm gonna get Jimmy back to Am
before she gets pissed.

47:16.176 --> 47:18.802
- I'll see you at the bar.
- Yeah.

47:18.885 --> 47:20.510
[Mac] All right, kid, let's go.

47:20.593 --> 47:22.969
Hey, you should bring him back.
He's got potential.

47:23.051 --> 47:25.635
[Mac] Hey, thanks,
anything you need.

47:25.719 --> 47:27.677
- How was it?
- Eh.

47:35.635 --> 47:36.802
I talked to Bridget.

47:36.885 --> 47:38.218
Yeah?

47:38.301 --> 47:40.176
Congratulations.

47:40.260 --> 47:42.301
Thanks.

47:42.385 --> 47:44.051
He's a good kid.

47:44.135 --> 47:46.635
Yeah, well, you know,
they're young.

47:46.719 --> 47:47.927
Well, you were young.

47:51.468 --> 47:53.010
You hear about Mick?

47:55.885 --> 47:58.510
Think we should fly
out there?

47:58.593 --> 48:00.802
What for?

48:00.885 --> 48:03.719
I don't know.
Say good-bye.

48:03.802 --> 48:06.093
Make sure we got no regrets.

48:08.844 --> 48:12.343
I don't got any regrets.
You?

48:12.427 --> 48:14.385
No.

48:14.468 --> 48:16.135
Fuck him.

48:27.260 --> 48:28.927
Mick.

48:31.760 --> 48:33.135
Mickey.

48:36.969 --> 48:38.218
Pop!

48:42.760 --> 48:44.427
What?

48:44.510 --> 48:47.885
Just making sure.

48:47.969 --> 48:51.051
Making sure what?

48:51.135 --> 48:54.301
I didn't break you out
so you could fucking die on me.

48:57.760 --> 48:59.969
[slowly] Ah, nah.

49:02.176 --> 49:04.135
I'm already a ghost, kid.

49:06.135 --> 49:08.844
I've been haunting people
all my life.

49:16.802 --> 49:19.468
♪ melancholy music ♪

49:19.552 --> 49:21.719
♪♪♪

49:21.802 --> 49:24.677
[boat horn blows]

49:24.760 --> 49:29.927
♪♪♪

49:43.301 --> 49:46.176
[cell phone ringing]

49:50.343 --> 49:52.927
[cell phone beeps]

49:53.010 --> 49:55.218
- Yeah?
- Mickey broke out.

49:55.301 --> 49:57.093
What?

49:57.176 --> 49:59.010
I don't know.
Bunchy must have helped him.

49:59.093 --> 50:01.135
Look, Ray, I don't know
what the fuck happened.

50:01.218 --> 50:03.218
But he almost killed
a fucking guard.

50:03.301 --> 50:07.093
So Bunchy's now not here,
and Mickey is out now.

50:07.176 --> 50:08.510
What are we gonna do?

50:10.427 --> 50:11.969
Ray?

50:13.510 --> 50:14.969
Yeah.

50:15.051 --> 50:18.051
A-are you okay?

50:18.135 --> 50:20.260
Sure.

50:20.343 --> 50:22.343
S-so what are we gonna do?

50:24.010 --> 50:26.593
Mickey is going to kill me.

50:26.677 --> 50:29.593
♪♪♪

50:29.677 --> 50:31.760
[line clicks]

50:31.844 --> 50:36.927
♪♪♪

50:40.051 --> 50:42.927
♪ reflective music ♪

50:43.010 --> 50:48.176
♪♪♪
